{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/notes/starship-prompt/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Chandler Moisen","author":"Chandler Moisen"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"82ac333f-28d5-538b-8c7a-4cd809bc5bfb","excerpt":"I have always wanted a tricked out command prompt, but have never invested much time in bash scripting aside from some simple functionality around git andâ€¦","html":"<p>I have always wanted a tricked out command prompt, but have never invested much time in bash scripting aside from some simple functionality around git and slight modifications to my prompt:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># Check if repo is dirty</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> parse_git_dirty<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">git</span> <span class=\"token function\">diff</span> --quiet --ignore-submodules HEAD 2<span class=\"token operator\">></span>/dev/null<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$?</span> -eq 1 <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">'*'</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Branch name</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> parse_git_branch<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">git</span> branch --no-color 2<span class=\"token operator\">></span> /dev/null <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sed</span> -e <span class=\"token string\">'/^[^*]/d'</span> -e <span class=\"token string\">\"s/* \\(.*\\)/\\1<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span>parse_git_dirty<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>/\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Prompt 1: \"username:\"</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">#PS1 is an environmental variable</span>\nPS1<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\\e[38;5;201m\\u\\e[0m âœŒ :\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Prompt 2: \"path/to/where/you/are\"</span>\nPS1<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$PS1</span>\\e[38;5;57m\\w\\e[0m\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Prompt 3: \"(gitbranch)\"</span>\nPS1<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$PS1</span> \\<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> -n \\<span class=\"token punctuation\">$(</span>git branch 2<span class=\"token operator\">></span> /dev/null<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span> ]] &amp;&amp; echo \\\" \\\")\\[\\033[1;33m\\]\\<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span>parse_git_branch<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\\[\\033[1;37m\\]\\n\\$ \\[<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span>tput sgr0<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\\]\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Luckily for me I recently came across <a href=\"https://starship.rs/\">Starship</a> - â€œthe minimal, blazing-fast and infinitely customizable prompt for any shell!â€</p>\n<p>Here is what my prompt looks like after setup and some basic configuration:</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3f9c550019f730ed901ead770f66613c/6feaa/starship_prompt.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 12.683823529411764%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAiklEQVQI152MvQoCMRAGd5NYnCS5aHeKgt6fp9iI4MPY+Aa+fzXmUoi1xbAw3zIS2o76NOEPLbEfSOcLVdMQfE2/6hnXI3u/495NvF9PHtcjoVpyGzZso9AEJcVIbBNxSIgag1qHcYty1diCqKJiMGoLNjtn580hohnJfv7JaG7kjpjihf/Qb/iXD8JSQxvNg9J+AAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Starship Prompt\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/3f9c550019f730ed901ead770f66613c/b9e4f/starship_prompt.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3f9c550019f730ed901ead770f66613c/cf440/starship_prompt.png 148w,\n/static/3f9c550019f730ed901ead770f66613c/d2d38/starship_prompt.png 295w,\n/static/3f9c550019f730ed901ead770f66613c/b9e4f/starship_prompt.png 590w,\n/static/3f9c550019f730ed901ead770f66613c/f9b6a/starship_prompt.png 885w,\n/static/3f9c550019f730ed901ead770f66613c/6feaa/starship_prompt.png 1088w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>Besides being incredibly simple to setup and get going, the customization aspect via a <code class=\"language-text\">.toml</code> file </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>character<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\nsymbol <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"âœ\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>git_status<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\nconflicted <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ğŸ³\"</span>\nahead <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ğŸğŸ’¨\"</span>\nbehind <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ğŸ˜°\"</span>\ndiverged <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ğŸ˜µ\"</span>\nuntracked <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ğŸ¤·&lt;U+200D>\"</span>\nstashed <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ğŸ“¦\"</span>\nmodified <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ğŸ“\"</span>\nstaged.value <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"++\"</span>\nstaged.style <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"green\"</span>\nstaged_count.enabled <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\nstaged_count.style <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"green\"</span>\nrenamed <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ğŸ‘…\"</span>\ndeleted <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ğŸ—‘\"</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Starship Prompt","date":"July 16, 2020","isTIL":true}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/starship-prompt/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/put-vs-patch/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"HTTP PUT vs PATCH","redirects":null}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech-ethic/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tech Ethic","redirects":null}}}}}